== 歷史 ==

2C-B由[[Alexander_Shulgin|Alexander Shulgin]]在1974年開發。惠於藥效短暫、性質溫和、副作用微弱的特性<ref name="erowid effects">{{cite web | url = http://www.erowid.org/chemicals/2cb/2cb_effects.shtml | title = Erowid 2C-B Vault: Effects | access-date = 2013-09-25 | publisher = [[Erowid|Erowid]] | archive-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210119124231/https://www.erowid.org/chemicals/2cb/2cb_effects.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>，2C-B被認為是治療[[精神疾病|精神疾病]]的特效藥之一而為醫學界所歡迎，不久即出現對2C-B的娛樂性使用。德國製藥企業[[Drittewelle|Drittewelle]]將2C-B以"Erox"<ref name="Reappears"/>的商品名作為[[春藥|春藥]]合法銷售<ref name='dritte pack'>{{cite web|title=Drittewelle 2C-B Packaging|url=https://www.erowid.org/chemicals/show_image.php?i=2cb/2cb_pack2.jpg|publisher=Erowid.org|accessdate=2013-09-25|year=2002|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504005802/https://www.erowid.org/chemicals/show_image.php?i=2cb%2F2cb_pack2.jpg|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此為2C-B的第一次商業應用。荷蘭境內的{{link-en|smart shop|smart shop}}一度有售諢名"Nexus"的2C-B片劑。

1994年12月20日,美国缉毒局（Drug Enforcement Administration）於''[[聯邦公報|聯邦公報]]''(Federal Register)發布立法建议，提議將2C-B歸入Schedule I管制。<ref name='fedreg'>{{cite journal | title = Schedules of Controlled Substances; Proposed Placement of 4-bromo-2,5-dimethoxyphenethylamine into Schedule I | journal = Federal Register | date = 1994-12-20 | volume = 59 | issue = 243 | page = 65521 | id =  | url = http://isomerdesign.com/Cdsa/FR/59FR65521.pdf | format = PDF | accessdate = 2013-09-26 | archive-date = 2020-10-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031125936/http://isomerdesign.com/Cdsa/FR/59FR65521.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>1995年7月2日，該法案開始永久生效。{{citation needed|date=September 2013}}

儘管無2C-B引致健康風險的報導，荷蘭仍將2C-B歸入鴉片法第一清單監控。相對地，{{link-en|2C-I|2C-I}}, {{link-en|2C-T-2|2C-T-2}}和{{link-en|2C-T-7|2C-T-7}}等衍生物陸續取代2C-B進入流通，直至荷蘭發行針對性禁令。

==流通==

自[[MDMA|MDMA]](Ecstasy)1985年被美國法令禁止後，2C-B開始取代MDMA流行街頭，許多銳舞(rave)愛好者將其誤認或作為"Ecstasy"出售，2C-B因而普及各國，廣受濫用。<ref name="Gahlinger book">{{cite book|last=Gahlinger|first=Paul|title=Illegal Drugs: A Complete Guide to Their History, Chemistry, Use and Abuse|year=2004|publisher=Penguin|isbn=9780452285057|pages=343–344|url=https://books.google.com/?id=kPszgXPVQAsC&pg=PT463&lpg=PT463#v=onepage&q&f=false}}</ref><ref name=Colombia>{{cite news|last=Pachico|first=Elyssa|title='2CB Now Drug of Choice for Colombia Elite'|url=http://www.insightcrime.org/news-analysis/2c-b-now-drug-of-choice-for-colombia-elite|accessdate=2013-02-11|newspaper=InSight Crime|date=2012-11-01|archive-date=2017-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925182840/http://www.insightcrime.org/news-analysis/2c-b-now-drug-of-choice-for-colombia-elite|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在美國境內，街頭兜售的2C-B片劑每片通常定價在$10至$30之間<ref name="DEA - Evaluation Section" /> ，大規模零售的2C-B價格從$200/g到$500/g不等，若批發銷售則價格進一步走低，於$100/g至$300/g間波動<ref name="Reappears">{{cite web|title=2C-B (Nexus) Reappears on the Club Drug Scene|url=http://www.justice.gov/archive/ndic/pubs0/665/665p.pdf|work=National Drug Intelligence Center|publisher=Department of Justice|accessdate=2013-02-11|date=May 2001|archive-date=2017-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170704062744/https://www.justice.gov/archive/ndic/pubs0/665/665p.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

